848
00:45:42,760 --> 00:45:45,239
[SPEAKER_01] I pojedinac koji ima visok HRV...

849
00:45:45,239 --> 00:45:45,880
[SPEAKER_00] Što je HRV?

850
00:45:45,880 --> 00:45:47,940
[SPEAKER_01] HRV, Heart Rate Variability.

851
