896
00:48:03,219 --> 00:48:04,159
[SPEAKER_00] Išteš na trening snage?

897
00:48:04,159 --> 00:48:05,659
[SPEAKER_01] Trening snage, da.

898
00:48:05,659 --> 00:48:08,099
