999
00:51:50,059 --> 00:51:52,679
[SPEAKER_00] Baja haker.

1000
00:51:52,679 --> 00:51:53,639
[SPEAKER_00] Ej, to želim naučiti.

1001
00:51:53,639 --> 00:51:54,300
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, da.

1002
00:51:54,300 --> 00:51:58,159
[SPEAKER_00] I onda znamo komentirati tako

1003
00:51:58,159 --> 00:52:02,460
