1008
00:52:08,659 --> 00:52:10,500
[SPEAKER_00] pio sam, ne znam,

1009
00:52:10,559 --> 00:52:12,079
[SPEAKER_00] nisam ništa trenirao ti jedan dana

1010
00:52:12,079 --> 00:52:12,719
[SPEAKER_00] ili tako dalje.

1011
00:52:12,719 --> 00:52:15,739
[SPEAKER_00] Da li ti sad u ovoj fazi svog života

1012
00:52:15,739 --> 00:52:17,780
[SPEAKER_00] imaš taj neki osjećaj grižnje,

1013
