[SPEAKER_01] Tako da ovih 15 minuta,

1027
00:52:45,599 --> 00:52:46,300
[SPEAKER_01] gledam u naprijed.

1028
00:52:46,300 --> 00:52:47,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ja znam da u srijedu,

1029
