1032
00:52:54,800 --> 00:52:56,599
[SPEAKER_01] minimalnog treninga kod kuće.

1033
00:52:56,599 --> 00:52:58,500
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, garant je tako.

1034
00:52:58,500 --> 00:52:59,400
[SPEAKER_01] I onda,

1035
