1620
01:31:50,140 --> 01:31:51,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam kako je.

1621
01:31:51,460 --> 01:31:53,260
[SPEAKER_01] Ma znam što, ne mogu sjetiti.

1622
01:31:53,340 --> 01:31:54,079
[SPEAKER_00] A, Tony Robbins.

1623
01:31:54,079 --> 01:31:54,500
