1624
01:31:54,500 --> 01:32:01,680
[SPEAKER_01] Isu se vidio, izlječio je mladog čovjeka od suicida, nećete vjerovat, spriječio je suicid.

1625
01:32:01,680 --> 01:32:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] U svega dvije, tri minute, u dvorani.

1626
01:32:08,500 --> 01:32:09,439
[SPEAKER_00] Pa kako?

1627
01:32:09,439 --> 01:32:11,539
[SPEAKER_01] A pa, neko nije odreagirao.

1628
01:32:11,539 --> 01:32:14,100
[SPEAKER_01] Kako bi se ja trebao osjećati onda,

1629
01:32:14,100 --> 01:32:16,880
[SPEAKER_01] ako se u moje obitelji to dogodilo,

1630
01:32:16,880 --> 01:32:20,260
[SPEAKER_01] frajer u tri minute lječi ovaj pogledom,

1631
01:32:20,260 --> 01:32:22,579
