1632
01:32:22,579 --> 01:32:23,239
[SPEAKER_01] i ne znam čim,

1633
01:32:23,239 --> 01:32:24,399
[SPEAKER_01] ovaj hladnom kupkom,

1634
01:32:24,699 --> 01:32:25,659
[SPEAKER_01] ljude od suicida,

1635
01:32:25,659 --> 01:32:27,039
[SPEAKER_01] ovaj ga je pogledao,

1636
01:32:27,039 --> 01:32:28,779
[SPEAKER_01] tri dobre, tople riječi uputio,

1637
01:32:28,779 --> 01:32:31,020
[SPEAKER_01] čovjek je odlučio da se neće ipak ubiti.

1638
01:32:31,020 --> 01:32:34,039
[SPEAKER_01] Jel, taj čovjek bio doistan sklon suicidu,

1639
01:32:34,039 --> 01:32:35,180
[SPEAKER_01] bio spreman se ubiti,

1640
01:32:35,180 --> 01:32:37,159
