1641
01:32:37,159 --> 01:32:39,739
[SPEAKER_01] jer ako je, ja bih molio Tonija

1642
01:32:39,739 --> 01:32:41,439
[SPEAKER_01] da organizira veliki summit

1643
01:32:41,439 --> 01:32:43,439
[SPEAKER_01] za sve suicidalne osobe,

1644
01:32:43,439 --> 01:32:44,420
[SPEAKER_01] da ih sve spasi.

1645
01:32:44,420 --> 01:32:47,039
[SPEAKER_01] Osim što Znanos kaže da to nije moguće.

1646
01:32:47,039 --> 01:32:48,880
[SPEAKER_01] Da su to teške budolaštine,

1647
01:32:48,880 --> 01:32:51,140
[SPEAKER_01] idiotarije koje štete obiteljima,

1648
01:32:51,140 --> 01:32:52,239
[SPEAKER_01] koje to gledaju i misle si,

1649
01:32:53,079 --> 01:32:55,039
[SPEAKER_01] jebote, pa i moj brat,

1650
01:32:55,039 --> 01:32:56,340
