1651
01:32:56,340 --> 01:32:57,500
[SPEAKER_01] svi su mogli živjeti,

1652
01:32:57,500 --> 01:32:59,619
[SPEAKER_01] da su Tonija pogledali na tri minute.

1653
01:32:59,619 --> 01:33:02,800
[SPEAKER_01] Kak bi se ti ljudi trebali osjećati?

1654
01:33:02,800 --> 01:33:05,680
[SPEAKER_01] Ili treba vjerovat da su i oni mogli,

1655
01:33:05,680 --> 01:33:07,079
[SPEAKER_01] onda ako Tony u tri minute,

1656
01:33:07,079 --> 01:33:07,779
[SPEAKER_01] ja u 30.

1657
01:33:07,779 --> 01:33:11,420
[SPEAKER_01] To je neodgovorno ponašanje,

1658
01:33:11,420 --> 01:33:12,460
