1659
01:33:12,460 --> 01:33:19,260
[SPEAKER_00] Malo sam se zapijenio, moram.

1660
01:33:19,260 --> 01:33:19,779
[SPEAKER_00] Neka si.

1661
01:33:19,779 --> 01:33:22,640
[SPEAKER_00] Neka si, dobro je to.

1662
01:33:23,079 --> 01:33:27,539
[SPEAKER_00] Koga bi osim Hubermana preporučio kao autora,

1663
01:33:27,539 --> 01:33:29,039
[SPEAKER_00] recimo, koje ti proučavaš

1664
01:33:29,039 --> 01:33:30,340
[SPEAKER_00] i koje,

1665
01:33:30,340 --> 01:33:32,819
[SPEAKER_00] ne samo da poštuješ,

1666
01:33:32,819 --> 01:33:35,199
[SPEAKER_00] nego vjeruješ njihovom radu.

1667
01:33:35,199 --> 01:33:36,659
[SPEAKER_01] Javno poznati ovako,

1668
01:33:36,659 --> 01:33:39,079
[SPEAKER_01] autori, pa ne znam, ono...

1669
01:33:39,079 --> 01:33:40,460
[SPEAKER_00] Šta ti, recimo,

1670
01:33:40,460 --> 01:33:41,439
[SPEAKER_00] konzumiraš?

1671
01:33:41,439 --> 01:33:44,060
[SPEAKER_00] Još kad si spomenio da bi bilo dobro

1672
01:33:44,060 --> 01:33:45,479
[SPEAKER_00] da kritički promišljamo,

1673
01:33:45,479 --> 01:33:47,260
[SPEAKER_00] osim hrane koju konzumiramo,

1674
01:33:47,260 --> 01:33:48,960
