1676
01:33:51,300 --> 01:33:52,720
[SPEAKER_00] to isto neka informacija, jel tako?

1677
01:33:52,720 --> 01:33:56,039
[SPEAKER_01] Nemam nekog koji bi sad tako autora istaknuo

1678
01:33:56,039 --> 01:33:58,739
[SPEAKER_01] i opće nepotrebno da sam i njega spomenuo.

1679
01:33:58,739 --> 01:34:00,060
[SPEAKER_01] Ne volim tako isticat sad,

1680
01:34:00,060 --> 01:34:01,359
[SPEAKER_01] jer onda to ispadne koda,

1681
01:34:01,359 --> 01:34:02,840
[SPEAKER_01] naš ono slušaj ovog li kao ti...

1682
01:34:02,840 --> 01:34:04,380
[SPEAKER_01] Kao da nekog pomoviraš.

1683
01:34:04,760 --> 01:34:06,840
[SPEAKER_01] nego ono što mogu reći samo ovako,

1684
01:34:06,840 --> 01:34:09,119
[SPEAKER_01] kad pročitam neku vijest,

1685
01:34:09,119 --> 01:34:11,859
[SPEAKER_01] a svi smo nemenovno izloženi razno raznim vijestima,

1686
01:34:11,859 --> 01:34:14,180
[SPEAKER_01] i kad se nešto prezentira kao znanstvena istina,

1687
01:34:14,180 --> 01:34:15,739
[SPEAKER_01] onda me zanima source.

1688
01:34:15,739 --> 01:34:17,760
[SPEAKER_01] Ono izvor, jel?

1689
01:34:17,760 --> 01:34:19,020
[SPEAKER_01] Znači ono što volim je,

1690
01:34:19,020 --> 01:34:21,939
[SPEAKER_01] volim je da su fakulteti upleteni,

1691
01:34:21,939 --> 01:34:24,300
[SPEAKER_01] znači znanstvene ustanove,

1692
01:34:24,300 --> 01:34:27,220
[SPEAKER_01] volim da su to mjesta ili ustanove koje

1693
01:34:27,220 --> 01:34:30,720
[SPEAKER_01] imaju čak sklonost prema takozvanoj ezoteriji

1694
01:34:30,720 --> 01:34:31,779
[SPEAKER_01] kao što je Mayo Klinika.

1695
01:34:31,779 --> 01:34:33,020
[SPEAKER_01] Jer da nje nema,

1696
01:34:33,020 --> 01:34:35,619
[SPEAKER_01] ne bi imali mindfulness meditaciju baš danas samo tako

1697
01:34:35,619 --> 01:34:37,539
[SPEAKER_01] i ne bi imali sva ta istraživanja

1698
01:34:37,539 --> 01:34:39,260
[SPEAKER_01] koja su vezane na psihologiju boli

1699
01:34:39,260 --> 01:34:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] ili ne znam čega.

1700
01:34:40,000 --> 01:34:42,319
[SPEAKER_01] Ali volim takve stvari.

1701
01:34:42,319 --> 01:34:44,699
[SPEAKER_01] Volim je da je neko istraživanje

1702
01:34:44,699 --> 01:34:47,760
[SPEAKER_01] endorsano od strane neke značajne ustanove.

1703
01:34:47,760 --> 01:34:49,840
[SPEAKER_01] Ili, ako nije,

1704
01:34:49,840 --> 01:34:52,539
[SPEAKER_01] aj bar da taj lik koje napravi istraživanje

1705
01:34:52,539 --> 01:34:54,359
[SPEAKER_01] koje u potpisu ima, ne znam, PhD.

1706
01:34:54,359 --> 01:34:55,319
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ja ga nemam.

1707
01:34:56,239 --> 01:34:58,520
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam sebi ne bih vjerovalo da napravim istraživanje.

1708
01:34:58,520 --> 01:35:01,680
[SPEAKER_01] Tražio bi podršku nekog koji je obrazovan

1709
01:35:01,680 --> 01:35:04,880
[SPEAKER_01] od strane ozbilne ustanove fakulteta

1710
01:35:04,880 --> 01:35:07,399
[SPEAKER_01] sa doktoratom da mi pomogne

1711
01:35:07,399 --> 01:35:08,199
[SPEAKER_01] da ja provjerim

1712
01:35:08,199 --> 01:35:10,979
[SPEAKER_01] je li to stvarno istraživanje ima smisla drži vodu.

1713
01:35:10,979 --> 01:35:13,239
[SPEAKER_01] Jer imati istraživanje

1714
01:35:13,239 --> 01:35:15,060
[SPEAKER_01] ne znači da je ono valjano i pouzdano.

1715
01:35:15,060 --> 01:35:18,359
[SPEAKER_01] Istraživanje postoje koje su katastrofične.

1716
01:35:18,359 --> 01:35:21,199
[SPEAKER_01] Ali treba znati, pročitati, treba i znati, vidjeti.

1717
01:35:21,199 --> 01:35:23,180
[SPEAKER_01] Zato je ono što predlažem svima je

1718
01:35:23,180 --> 01:35:26,039
[SPEAKER_01] daj pogledaj izvor od kud je došlo.

1719
01:35:26,239 --> 01:35:28,680
[SPEAKER_00] Moje mišljenje, moje stave je da

1720
01:35:28,680 --> 01:35:34,479
[SPEAKER_00] kroz recimo, pogotovo od kad je recimo COVID-19 krenio,

1721
01:35:36,479 --> 01:35:40,479
[SPEAKER_00] sad imaš Elon Muska kao recimo nekakvu globalnu dinamiku.

1722
01:35:40,479 --> 01:35:44,079
[SPEAKER_00] On je kupio Twitter za jako puno novaca.

1723
01:35:44,079 --> 01:35:48,359
[SPEAKER_00] On je počeo, imaš onaj slučaj koji se zove Twitter Files.

1724
01:35:48,359 --> 01:35:51,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam da li si čuo za to je slučaj.

1725
01:35:51,220 --> 01:36:00,399
[SPEAKER_00] Uglavno gdje je on sada javno obznanio da je američka vlada plus FBI da su imali pristup Twitteru,

1726
01:36:00,399 --> 01:36:05,819
[SPEAKER_00] čak i privatnim porukama unutar Twittera, da su imali uvid u sve to.

1727
01:36:05,819 --> 01:36:08,420
[SPEAKER_00] Znači to je on javno objavio.

1728
01:36:08,420 --> 01:36:17,539
[SPEAKER_00] I sad imao je neki dan intervju recimo i sa BBCM gdje ti imaš takve medijske mega kompanije

1729
01:36:17,539 --> 01:36:24,380
[SPEAKER_00] koje stvaraju javno mišljenje i utječu na djelovanje, na ponašanje ljudi.

1730
01:36:25,880 --> 01:36:31,039
[SPEAKER_00] Nažalost, u nekim trenucima su lažno informirali javno.

1731
01:36:31,039 --> 01:36:36,319
[SPEAKER_00] Sad neću ja ulaziti u nekakve teorije zavir ili šta da znam sad u ovom trenutku,

1732
01:36:36,319 --> 01:36:44,220
[SPEAKER_00] ali postoji nekakav prijelomna točka recimo u društvu, u zapadnom svijetu,

1733
01:36:44,220 --> 01:36:47,539
[SPEAKER_00] ja bih rekao možda tako da se precizni izrazim, u zadnjih par godina,

1734
01:36:48,140 --> 01:36:56,439
[SPEAKER_00] kada je društvo počelo više sumnjati u institucije i u one koji nas vode.

1735
01:36:56,439 --> 01:37:02,560
[SPEAKER_00] To je jedna od stvari, a druga od stvari je što naravno kad si očajan

1736
01:37:02,560 --> 01:37:07,760
[SPEAKER_00] i kad pokušavaš ići kod lješnika, svečnika, ono što ja znam, koga na koga si naučio,

1737
01:37:07,760 --> 01:37:11,279
[SPEAKER_00] ti ti više ne pomažu, li su ti ukrenuli leđe,

1738
01:37:11,279 --> 01:37:17,239
[SPEAKER_00] onda ideš i kod brace koji te gleda u oči i ideš kod nekih drugih ljudi

1739
01:37:17,239 --> 01:37:23,420
[SPEAKER_00] kao što je Ante Palović bio, koji je centrirao ljude.

1740
01:37:23,420 --> 01:37:32,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ja da sam teško, terminalno bolestan i pitao bi ja i braco za pomoć,

1741
01:37:32,539 --> 01:37:38,100
[SPEAKER_01] svakog bi to za pomoć, ali ja osoba ne bih mogao tvrditi,

1742
01:37:38,100 --> 01:37:41,880
[SPEAKER_01] ja kao psiholog, kao neko ko radi taj posao svaki dan,

1743
01:37:41,880 --> 01:37:46,159
[SPEAKER_01] imam neku diplomu koja stoji za mene, ja ne mogu tvrditi da ću ja pomoć svakom.

1744
01:37:46,340 --> 01:37:51,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ne mogu i ne mogu reći da je sve za svakog, nije ni meditacija za svakog.

1745
01:37:51,500 --> 01:37:54,159
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala Bogu, znanost je to rekla da nije za svakog.

1746
01:37:54,159 --> 01:38:00,619
[SPEAKER_01] Sad imaš problem s depresijom, samo meditire, pa najvjerojatnije ćeš ruminirati nad vlastiti mislima,

1747
01:38:00,619 --> 01:38:03,520
[SPEAKER_01] je li tako što nije veliki hit za depresiju.

1748
01:38:04,359 --> 01:38:09,520
[SPEAKER_01] Ja samo to hoću reći da čak i kad imamo znanstvene dokaze za nešto da funkcionira,

1749
01:38:09,520 --> 01:38:12,500
[SPEAKER_01] funkcionira, to ne znači da je univerzalno.

1750
01:38:12,500 --> 01:38:17,479
[SPEAKER_01] Jer znanost kaže za većinu, znamo kako izgleda gaussova krivulja,

1751
01:38:17,479 --> 01:38:23,779
[SPEAKER_01] znači da pogađa većinu ili moraš da nikog ne pogađa, jer je ljevo i desno su ljudi od krivulje.

1752
01:38:24,779 --> 01:38:27,479
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ovo je lupan bez veze.

1753
01:38:27,479 --> 01:38:32,180
[SPEAKER_01] Super je, i mene je drago da takve stvari opet ponavljam postoje,

1754
01:38:32,180 --> 01:38:38,039
[SPEAKER_01] jer drže vodu djelomečno, ali ja ih ne mogu gurat kao znanstvenu istinu,

1755
01:38:38,039 --> 01:38:41,079
[SPEAKER_01] trenutni dokaz, dok još to nije baš tako.

1756
01:38:41,079 --> 01:38:42,340
[SPEAKER_01] Ali eto.

1757
01:38:42,340 --> 01:38:43,520
[SPEAKER_01] Ok.

1758
01:38:43,520 --> 01:38:45,460
[SPEAKER_00] Za kraj,

1759
01:38:45,460 --> 01:38:53,460
[SPEAKER_00] htio bih da malo elaboriraš ove vrijednosti koje si nabrao na početku našeg razgovora,

1760
01:38:53,460 --> 01:38:56,600
[SPEAKER_00] ljubav, sloboda, patnja, si tako rekao bih, je li?

1761
01:38:56,600 --> 01:38:59,539
[SPEAKER_01] Red, rad, disciplina, ljubav, sloboda i patnja.

1762
01:38:59,539 --> 01:39:02,619
[SPEAKER_01] Da, mojih šest temeljnih.

1763
01:39:02,619 --> 01:39:05,579
[SPEAKER_00] Red, rad, disciplina, ok, to možemo staviti pod isti nazivnik.

1764
01:39:05,579 --> 01:39:07,720
[SPEAKER_00] A to je, da, odgoj, sport.

1765
01:39:07,720 --> 01:39:09,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ljubav, sloboda, patnja.

1766
01:39:09,159 --> 01:39:12,220
[SPEAKER_00] Šta, to su tvoje vrijednosti, je tako?

1767
01:39:12,220 --> 01:39:14,619
[SPEAKER_01] Da, moje temeljne. Jedna od, nije to sve.

1768
01:39:14,619 --> 01:39:16,720
[SPEAKER_01] Nisu sve, jedna od temeljnih, ok.

1769
01:39:16,720 --> 01:39:17,800
[SPEAKER_01] Na koje se podsjeća.

1770
01:39:17,800 --> 01:39:24,260
[SPEAKER_00] Kako bih opisao uopće? Šta stoji za ljubavi, ono, tvojim riječima? Šta stoji za slobode, šta stoji za patnje?

1771
01:39:25,260 --> 01:39:32,140
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala ti što me nisi poslao pripremu, da se pripremim za ovakve odgovore, pa ovako mogu biti spontan.

1772
01:39:32,140 --> 01:39:33,720
[SPEAKER_01] Odlično, igramo se i dalje.

1773
01:39:33,720 --> 01:39:34,119
[SPEAKER_01] Igramo se.

1774
01:39:34,119 --> 01:39:40,159
[SPEAKER_01] Ljubav, ljubav za mene, ljubav za mene je nešto, zapravo ljubav je apsolutno sve.

1775
01:39:40,159 --> 01:39:41,939
[SPEAKER_01] Ništa već od ljubavi ne postoji.

1776
01:39:41,939 --> 01:39:43,300
[SPEAKER_00] To je znanstveno utemeljeno?

1777
01:39:43,300 --> 01:39:43,579
[SPEAKER_01] Ne.

1778
01:39:43,579 --> 01:39:47,020
[SPEAKER_00] Kako si mi duskučio, a?

1779
01:39:47,020 --> 01:39:55,479
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, u našim vrijednostima ne tražimo ni dobro, ni zlo, ni znanost, ni ezoteriju.

1780
01:39:55,479 --> 01:40:00,899
[SPEAKER_01] One su, kao što Elvis rekao, otisci prstiju koju ostavljamo svugdje za sobom.

1781
01:40:00,899 --> 01:40:03,439
[SPEAKER_01] Svako od nas ima svoj različit set.

1782
01:40:03,439 --> 01:40:05,600
[SPEAKER_01] Tako ja gledam na ovo.

1783
01:40:05,600 --> 01:40:08,539
[SPEAKER_01] Moje vrijednosti opisuju samo moje djelovanja.

1784
01:40:08,539 --> 01:40:11,340
[SPEAKER_01] Ja vjerujem u ljubav, vjerujem da smo sposobni davati ljubav.

1785
01:40:11,340 --> 01:40:16,699
[SPEAKER_01] Zato nemam dokaz, osim iskustva kao što ga ima Wim Hof.

1786
01:40:17,020 --> 01:40:21,840
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ljubav mi je totalno cool stvar.

1787
01:40:21,840 --> 01:40:24,399
[SPEAKER_01] Zato što dogod se uspijem usmjeriti na nju,

1788
01:40:24,399 --> 01:40:27,140
[SPEAKER_01] bolje funkcioniram u razno raznim odnosima,

1789
01:40:27,140 --> 01:40:28,899
[SPEAKER_01] bolje funkcioniram sa klijentima.

1790
01:40:28,899 --> 01:40:32,199
[SPEAKER_01] Ljubav sama po sebi ne bi trebala imati granice.

1791
01:40:32,199 --> 01:40:33,920
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je bezuvjetna po definiciji.

1792
01:40:33,920 --> 01:40:37,720
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da je zakon, ona je slobodna, znanosti čak.

1793
01:40:37,720 --> 01:40:39,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je iznad apsolutno svega.

1794
01:40:39,539 --> 01:40:41,720
[SPEAKER_01] Ljubav je, kažem, ono, apsolutno sve.

1795
01:40:41,720 --> 01:40:44,779
[SPEAKER_01] Sad neki katolici i vjernici bi se sa mnom složili,

1796
01:40:44,859 --> 01:40:47,619
[SPEAKER_01] ali ne idem u smjeru samo ljubavi u skladu s vjerom,

1797
01:40:47,619 --> 01:40:49,500
[SPEAKER_01] iako vjerujem da ćemo se dobro složiti.

1798
01:40:49,500 --> 01:40:52,699
[SPEAKER_01] Ja samo vjerujem da je to nešto što nas potencijalno spaja,

1799
01:40:52,699 --> 01:40:56,100
[SPEAKER_01] ali je toliko močno da nas i potencijalno razvaja

1800
01:40:56,100 --> 01:40:58,539
[SPEAKER_01] u trenutcima kad ne volimo jedne druge.

1801
01:40:58,779 --> 01:41:02,159
[SPEAKER_01] I kad ta ljubav dopoprima onaj neki negativni preznik,

1802
01:41:02,159 --> 01:41:03,020
[SPEAKER_01] zove se mržnja,

1803
01:41:03,020 --> 01:41:07,159
[SPEAKER_01] a zapravo bez neke druge ljubavi to ne bi bilo moguće.

1804
01:41:07,159 --> 01:41:09,039
[SPEAKER_01] Toga ljubav mi je totalno cool stvar

1805
01:41:09,039 --> 01:41:10,619
[SPEAKER_01] i bez nje osobno,

1806
01:41:10,619 --> 01:41:13,819
[SPEAKER_01] ne predlažem drugima, ne bi mogo funkcionirati.

1807
01:41:13,819 --> 01:41:16,659
[SPEAKER_01] Što se tiče slobode,

1808
01:41:16,659 --> 01:41:18,899
[SPEAKER_01] ona mi je bila bitna ako klincu od uvijek,

1809
01:41:18,899 --> 01:41:20,460
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam, to me sam jako naginio.

1810
01:41:20,460 --> 01:41:23,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ne znam, to zbog društva u kojem sam odrasto,

1811
01:41:23,659 --> 01:41:26,159
[SPEAKER_01] pa mi to bilo ono jako bitno da imamo slobodu govora,

1812
01:41:26,159 --> 01:41:28,319
[SPEAKER_01] slobodu izričaja, ne znam što,

1813
01:41:28,319 --> 01:41:30,979
[SPEAKER_01] ali mi je jako bilo bitno tako da sam svoje

1814
01:41:30,979 --> 01:41:33,460
[SPEAKER_01] tinerđerske godine proveo kao punker,

1815
01:41:33,460 --> 01:41:35,180
[SPEAKER_01] imao sam u nekom trenutku i rokezu.

1816
01:41:35,180 --> 01:41:36,960
[SPEAKER_00] Neki dan sam tek vidio njegove slike.

1817
01:41:36,960 --> 01:41:39,060
[SPEAKER_01] Imao sam crvenu kosu, zelenu kosu,

1818
01:41:39,060 --> 01:41:40,479
[SPEAKER_01] rozu kosu, bez kose,

1819
01:41:40,479 --> 01:41:42,579
[SPEAKER_01] imao sam apsolutno sve bodlje oko vrata,

1820
01:41:42,579 --> 01:41:43,600
[SPEAKER_01] bodlje oko ruke.

1821
01:41:43,600 --> 01:41:46,920
[SPEAKER_01] Sve sam probao, igle na glavi i tako.

1822
01:41:46,920 --> 01:41:48,239
[SPEAKER_01] Nije to dugo trajalo,

1823
01:41:48,239 --> 01:41:50,039
[SPEAKER_01] ali to je bilo moje neko buntovništvo

1824
01:41:50,039 --> 01:41:51,819
[SPEAKER_01] i prakticiranje slobode.

1825
01:41:53,659 --> 01:41:55,880
[SPEAKER_01] Sloboda mi je bitna i ona mi omogućava

1826
01:41:55,880 --> 01:41:57,779
[SPEAKER_01] izričaj, ali sad tu naravno

1827
01:41:57,779 --> 01:41:59,560
[SPEAKER_01] bilo bi dobro da piše odgovornost,

1828
01:41:59,560 --> 01:42:00,880
[SPEAKER_01] kao što je rekao Viktor Frankl,

1829
01:42:00,880 --> 01:42:03,539
[SPEAKER_01] jer sloboda i odgovornosti idu jedna

1830
01:42:03,539 --> 01:42:04,960
[SPEAKER_01] s drugom ruku pod ruku,

1831
01:42:04,960 --> 01:42:08,079
[SPEAKER_01] bez slobode ne želim biti odgovoran,

1832
01:42:08,079 --> 01:42:10,960
[SPEAKER_01] bez odgovornosti mi nije bitno biti slobodan,

1833
01:42:10,960 --> 01:42:12,260
[SPEAKER_01] jer onda to ide u smjeru anarhije,

1834
01:42:12,260 --> 01:42:13,699
[SPEAKER_01] to je ovo zašto sam imao i rokezu,

1835
01:42:13,699 --> 01:42:16,260
[SPEAKER_01] kasnije se shvatio da nije loša ta odgovornost,

1836
01:42:16,260 --> 01:42:18,039
[SPEAKER_01] toliko je, jer nas stavlja u balans.

1837
01:42:18,039 --> 01:42:20,140
[SPEAKER_01] A što se tiče patnje,

1838
01:42:20,199 --> 01:42:21,420
[SPEAKER_01] to me uvijek svi pita zašto patnje,

1839
01:42:21,420 --> 01:42:22,979
[SPEAKER_01] zašto patnje, ne znam ni ja zašto,

1840
01:42:22,979 --> 01:42:25,500
[SPEAKER_01] ali spada da kroz živog tražim stvari

1841
01:42:25,500 --> 01:42:28,600
[SPEAKER_01] koje su teške, čak na nivou fizičke boli,

1842
01:42:28,600 --> 01:42:30,399
[SPEAKER_01] zato sam se valjda bavio plivanjem,

1843
01:42:30,399 --> 01:42:32,279
[SPEAKER_01] toliko je izazovne,

1844
01:42:32,279 --> 01:42:34,920
[SPEAKER_01] da je patnja sastavni dio aktivnosti

1845
01:42:34,920 --> 01:42:36,460
[SPEAKER_01] i onda kad je, onda ja smatram

1846
01:42:36,460 --> 01:42:39,159
[SPEAKER_01] iz nekog svog iracionalnog razloga

1847
01:42:39,159 --> 01:42:41,319
[SPEAKER_01] tu aktivnost posebno važnom

1848
01:42:41,319 --> 01:42:44,680
[SPEAKER_01] ili bitnom ili dobrom ili tako nešto.

1849
01:42:44,680 --> 01:42:47,899
[SPEAKER_01] I dobro, tu nisam inovativan

1850
01:42:47,899 --> 01:42:51,779
[SPEAKER_01] kad kažem da patnja može dati smisao života ljudima

1851
01:42:51,779 --> 01:42:55,399
[SPEAKER_01] i u patnji je smisao nekima od nas.

1852
01:42:55,399 --> 01:42:58,819
[SPEAKER_01] To je nekao isto tako Viktor Frankl

1853
01:42:58,819 --> 01:43:01,720
[SPEAKER_01] kojeg kao autora, recimo, volim citirati.

1854
01:43:03,659 --> 01:43:05,859
[SPEAKER_00] Da li više voliš ovu nametnutu patnju

1855
01:43:05,859 --> 01:43:09,340
[SPEAKER_00] ili vlaststvo odabranu?

1856
01:43:09,340 --> 01:43:10,619
[SPEAKER_01] Odabranu, ako može.

1857
01:43:10,619 --> 01:43:13,479
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, možemo naći, ali to je onda baš potraga.

1858
01:43:13,479 --> 01:43:14,680
[SPEAKER_01] To je, ako što vam pisao knjigu

1859
01:43:14,680 --> 01:43:15,920
[SPEAKER_01] Potraga za smislam, jel?

1860
01:43:15,920 --> 01:43:17,319
[SPEAKER_01] Men Search for Meaning.

1861
01:43:17,319 --> 01:43:21,779
[SPEAKER_01] To je totalno druga priča.

1862
01:43:21,779 --> 01:43:23,579
[SPEAKER_01] Ja, ako sam izložen patnje

1863
01:43:23,579 --> 01:43:24,579
[SPEAKER_01] koju nisam planirao,

1864
01:43:24,579 --> 01:43:26,159
[SPEAKER_01] nisam se svjesno i namirno stavio

1865
01:43:26,159 --> 01:43:27,800
[SPEAKER_01] u određen set okolnosti,

1866
01:43:27,800 --> 01:43:30,159
[SPEAKER_01] ta potraga za smislom kroz patnju je

1867
01:43:30,159 --> 01:43:31,539
[SPEAKER_01] jako teška.

1868
01:43:31,539 --> 01:43:33,520
[SPEAKER_01] Nikom ni sebi to ne preporučam,

1869
01:43:33,619 --> 01:43:35,140
[SPEAKER_01] niti priželjkujem, pardon.

1870
01:43:35,140 --> 01:43:37,479
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ono izlaganje neka,

1871
01:43:37,479 --> 01:43:39,199
[SPEAKER_01] meni i ljudima koji su meni slični,

1872
01:43:39,199 --> 01:43:41,880
[SPEAKER_01] izlaganje aktivnostima koje podrazumijeve

1873
01:43:41,880 --> 01:43:44,239
[SPEAKER_01] neku dozu ili mentalne ili tjelesne patnje

1874
01:43:44,239 --> 01:43:46,380
[SPEAKER_01] za mene znači jako puno.

1875
01:43:46,380 --> 01:43:48,979
[SPEAKER_01] Ne uspjeh nužno u tim aktivnostima,

1876
01:43:48,979 --> 01:43:50,539
[SPEAKER_01] ali sladavanje aktivnosti

1877
01:43:50,539 --> 01:43:52,300
[SPEAKER_01] i na kraju naravno i završetak

1878
01:43:52,300 --> 01:43:53,300
[SPEAKER_01] aktivnosti patnje,

1879
01:43:53,300 --> 01:43:55,779
[SPEAKER_01] za mene sigurno predstavlja neki oblek

1880
01:43:55,779 --> 01:43:57,439
[SPEAKER_01] ili uspjeha ili postignuća

1881
01:43:57,439 --> 01:44:00,560
[SPEAKER_01] ili može čak i jednu dozu duhovnosti.

1882
01:44:00,560 --> 01:44:02,100
[SPEAKER_01] Ali u tu temu ne stignemo danas.

1883
01:44:02,119 --> 01:44:03,479
[SPEAKER_00] Ti imaš nekih šalabakterku?

1884
01:44:03,479 --> 01:44:05,319
[SPEAKER_00] Teo god da te neko pripremio za pitanje.

1885
01:44:05,319 --> 01:44:06,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, stvarno nije.

1886
01:44:06,460 --> 01:44:07,939
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo bi lijepo da je, ponavljam.

1887
01:44:07,939 --> 01:44:10,260
[SPEAKER_01] Ali evo, šta je, još imamo neku temu.

1888
01:44:10,260 --> 01:44:11,960
[SPEAKER_01] Reko se zadnji put, da je bilo zadnje.

1889
01:44:12,340 --> 01:44:14,560
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo zadnje, zadnje pitanje.

1890
01:44:14,560 --> 01:44:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja o tome često razmišljam u zadnje vrijeme.

1891
01:44:18,000 --> 01:44:23,079
[SPEAKER_00] Pa nemam nekakav pametan odgovor.

1892
01:44:23,079 --> 01:44:25,420
[SPEAKER_00] Znam, u teoriji, u praksi, još uvijek nisam

1893
01:44:25,420 --> 01:44:28,279
[SPEAKER_00] shvatio kako da se postavim prema tomu

1894
01:44:28,279 --> 01:44:29,359
[SPEAKER_00] ili kako da se ponašam.

1895
01:44:32,800 --> 01:44:36,079
[SPEAKER_00] Kakav je tvoj pristup prema tvojoj vlastitoj smrti?

1896
01:44:36,079 --> 01:44:37,399
[SPEAKER_01] Smrti?

1897
01:44:37,399 --> 01:44:41,159
[SPEAKER_01] Pa se mogu neko lakše pitanje zaprati.

1898
01:44:41,159 --> 01:44:42,760
[SPEAKER_00] Pa rekao si da voliš patnju, pa još idem

1899
01:44:42,760 --> 01:44:44,619
[SPEAKER_00] u skladu s ovom što ti voliš.

1900
01:44:44,619 --> 01:44:46,659
[SPEAKER_01] Pa li sam sa smrću prestaje svaka patnja.

1901
01:44:46,659 --> 01:44:47,979
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, ajmo ovako.

1902
01:44:47,979 --> 01:44:51,119
[SPEAKER_00] Idemo prije smrti, prije smrti ću te ovako.

1903
01:44:51,119 --> 01:44:53,880
[SPEAKER_00] Stara doba, približavaš se tome.

1904
01:44:53,880 --> 01:44:56,779
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ja planiram živi 120 godine

1905
01:44:56,779 --> 01:44:58,899
[SPEAKER_01] neka istraživanja pokazuju da imam kapacitet.

1906
01:44:58,899 --> 01:44:59,220
[SPEAKER_01] 120.

1907
01:44:59,220 --> 01:45:02,899
[SPEAKER_01] Neki kažu da bi mogli 120.

1908
01:45:02,899 --> 01:45:03,880
[SPEAKER_01] Ko je to rekao? Wim Hof?

1909
01:45:03,880 --> 01:45:06,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ne znam, to je rekla moja supruga, ona je čitala istraživanja

1910
01:45:06,659 --> 01:45:07,979
[SPEAKER_01] i joj bezuvjetno vjerujem.

1911
01:45:10,140 --> 01:45:14,699
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, da li osjećaš strah

1912
01:45:14,699 --> 01:45:16,819
[SPEAKER_00] ili nekakvu, možda drugu

1913
01:45:16,819 --> 01:45:18,979
[SPEAKER_00] negativnu emociju prema staroj dobi,

1914
01:45:18,979 --> 01:45:20,579
[SPEAKER_00] staroj dobi

1915
01:45:20,579 --> 01:45:22,699
[SPEAKER_00] uz koju ide i bolest

1916
01:45:22,699 --> 01:45:24,380
[SPEAKER_00] nekakav, može bitno,

1917
01:45:24,380 --> 01:45:26,939
[SPEAKER_00] i onda konačno zaošetak

1918
01:45:26,939 --> 01:45:29,039
[SPEAKER_00] te stare dobi i bolesti, to je smrt.

1919
01:45:29,039 --> 01:45:32,699
[SPEAKER_00] Kaki su ti osjećaj

1920
01:45:32,699 --> 01:45:33,979
[SPEAKER_00] ili...

1921
01:45:33,979 --> 01:45:36,039
[SPEAKER_00] Kako planiraš to?

1922
01:45:36,039 --> 01:45:38,300
[SPEAKER_01] Koži, prvo ću biti sažet.

1923
01:45:38,300 --> 01:45:39,960
[SPEAKER_01] Prvo, strah osjećam i sključivo.

1924
01:45:40,119 --> 01:45:42,359
[SPEAKER_01] prema ideji da postoji još jedno pitanje nakon ovog.

1925
01:45:42,359 --> 01:45:45,640
[SPEAKER_01] A što se tiče straha od smrti i starosti,

1926
01:45:45,640 --> 01:45:47,920
[SPEAKER_01] ovako,

1927
01:45:47,920 --> 01:45:50,079
[SPEAKER_01] nemam strah od starosti,

1928
01:45:50,079 --> 01:45:52,260
[SPEAKER_01] zato što mislim da se radi o sazrijevanju,

1929
01:45:52,260 --> 01:45:54,899
[SPEAKER_01] koje ne izgleda uvijek najljepše,

1930
01:45:54,899 --> 01:45:57,239
[SPEAKER_01] ali općenito stvari s godinama

1931
01:45:57,239 --> 01:45:58,680
[SPEAKER_01] ne moraju se svima svidjeti,

1932
01:45:58,680 --> 01:46:02,039
[SPEAKER_01] ali nose nešto i dobro i loše sa sobom.

1933
01:46:02,420 --> 01:46:04,939
[SPEAKER_01] ono čega me je strah,

1934
01:46:04,939 --> 01:46:09,460
[SPEAKER_01] da, je kako će ta starost izgledati po pitanju mog zdravlja.

1935
01:46:10,760 --> 01:46:13,439
[SPEAKER_01] fizičko, da, brine me, ne da me brine,

1936
01:46:13,439 --> 01:46:15,159
[SPEAKER_01] ne razmišljam pretirano o tome,

1937
01:46:15,159 --> 01:46:17,159
[SPEAKER_01] ali kad bi sad išao razmišljati,

1938
01:46:17,159 --> 01:46:19,119
[SPEAKER_01] da, to bi bila sigurno neka mala briga

1939
01:46:19,119 --> 01:46:22,119
[SPEAKER_01] i zato možda skrbim o svom zdravlju koliko god mogu.

1940
01:46:23,000 --> 01:46:25,180
[SPEAKER_01] Mentama me iskreno više brine,

1941
01:46:25,180 --> 01:46:26,539
[SPEAKER_01] ako ćemo o brizi,

1942
01:46:26,539 --> 01:46:27,779
[SPEAKER_01] zato što, ne znam,

1943
01:46:27,779 --> 01:46:30,479
[SPEAKER_01] volio bi biti čiste glave dok god sam živa.

1944
01:46:30,479 --> 01:46:33,220
[SPEAKER_01] Sad znam da to nije baš najrealnija ideja,

1945
01:46:33,220 --> 01:46:34,479
[SPEAKER_01] ali ajmo vidjeti,

1946
01:46:34,479 --> 01:46:35,520
[SPEAKER_01] i za to se trudim.

1947
01:46:35,520 --> 01:46:37,520
[SPEAKER_01] Što se smrti tiče,

1948
01:46:37,520 --> 01:46:40,439
[SPEAKER_01] strah me, naravno kao što je i većinu ljudi,

1949
01:46:40,439 --> 01:46:41,539
[SPEAKER_01] strah smrti,

1950
01:46:41,539 --> 01:46:43,239
[SPEAKER_01] ali me nije tako jako strah

1951
01:46:43,239 --> 01:46:46,399
[SPEAKER_01] ako se događa u nekoj tamo dalekoj budućnosti.

1952
01:46:46,399 --> 01:46:47,140
[SPEAKER_01] Strah me,

1953
01:46:47,140 --> 01:46:49,300
[SPEAKER_01] kad bi se tako nešto,

1954
01:46:49,300 --> 01:46:50,199
[SPEAKER_01] ili nije me strah,

1955
01:46:50,199 --> 01:46:51,479
[SPEAKER_01] nego mi je ružna pomisa,

1956
01:46:51,479 --> 01:46:52,420
[SPEAKER_01] užas mi je.

1957
01:46:53,000 --> 01:46:55,439
[SPEAKER_01] ideja da bi se tako nešto dogodi

1958
01:46:55,439 --> 01:46:56,439
[SPEAKER_01] prerano.

1959
01:46:56,439 --> 01:46:59,140
[SPEAKER_01] A po tim mislim,

1960
01:46:59,140 --> 01:47:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] čak, moram biti iskren,

1961
01:47:01,000 --> 01:47:02,060
[SPEAKER_01] nije me toliko sebe,

1962
01:47:02,060 --> 01:47:03,760
[SPEAKER_01] strah je malo,

1963
01:47:03,760 --> 01:47:04,779
[SPEAKER_01] ali više ono,

1964
01:47:04,779 --> 01:47:06,760
[SPEAKER_01] kaj će biti s drugima,

1965
01:47:06,760 --> 01:47:08,880
[SPEAKER_01] kako će to utjecat na moju djecu,

1966
01:47:08,880 --> 01:47:11,159
[SPEAKER_01] na suprugu,

1967
01:47:11,159 --> 01:47:12,659
[SPEAKER_01] na, ne znam, prijatelje,

1968
01:47:12,659 --> 01:47:13,619
[SPEAKER_01] užas.

1969
01:47:13,619 --> 01:47:16,319
[SPEAKER_01] To mi je deset puta gore

1970
01:47:16,319 --> 01:47:17,340
[SPEAKER_01] nego sama ideja smrti.

1971
01:47:17,340 --> 01:47:18,500
[SPEAKER_01] Stvarno vjerujem da nije ništa

1972
01:47:18,500 --> 01:47:19,520
[SPEAKER_01] tako strašno kasnije,

1973
01:47:19,520 --> 01:47:20,939
[SPEAKER_01] ovoga,

1974
01:47:20,939 --> 01:47:22,699
[SPEAKER_01] ali ne znam šta je.

1975
01:47:23,000 --> 01:47:24,439
[SPEAKER_01] ali ovaj,

1976
01:47:24,439 --> 01:47:25,699
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam,

1977
01:47:25,699 --> 01:47:27,119
[SPEAKER_01] samo da to sve skupa,

1978
01:47:27,119 --> 01:47:29,159
[SPEAKER_01] nek dođe čim kasnije,

1979
01:47:29,159 --> 01:47:31,239
[SPEAKER_01] tim bolje i da do tog trenutka

1980
01:47:31,239 --> 01:47:33,060
[SPEAKER_01] sve bude relativno ok.

1981
01:47:33,060 --> 01:47:34,800
[SPEAKER_01] tako da ne razmišljam puno o tome,

1982
01:47:34,800 --> 01:47:37,319
[SPEAKER_01] nego više pragmatično uložen.

1983
01:47:37,319 --> 01:47:38,739
[SPEAKER_00] šta kaže znanost o smrti.

1984
01:47:39,739 --> 01:47:41,439
[SPEAKER_00] ili još nismo dokućeni.

1985
01:47:41,439 --> 01:47:42,619
[SPEAKER_01] nema baš neki sanj odgovor,

1986
01:47:42,619 --> 01:47:46,100
[SPEAKER_01] osim da se i software i hardware gase,

1987
01:47:46,100 --> 01:47:48,079
[SPEAKER_01] a to mi se nikako ne svi,

1988
01:47:48,079 --> 01:47:50,359
[SPEAKER_01] to je najdješta je znanost došla.

1989
01:47:50,359 --> 01:47:51,579
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, koliko ja znam, ne znam.

1990
01:47:51,880 --> 01:47:57,539
[SPEAKER_00] znači, ipak postoji jako puno nekakih pojava u životu.

1991
01:47:57,539 --> 01:47:58,039
[SPEAKER_00] Apsolutno.

1992
01:47:58,039 --> 01:48:00,619
[SPEAKER_00] U našoj stvarnosti koje znanost nije dotaknila.

1993
01:48:00,619 --> 01:48:01,100
[SPEAKER_00] Još.

1994
01:48:01,100 --> 01:48:03,520
[SPEAKER_00] Zato i postoji tu i postoji religije,

1995
01:48:03,520 --> 01:48:04,720
[SPEAKER_00] postoje neke druge stvari,

1996
01:48:04,720 --> 01:48:06,579
[SPEAKER_00] postoji i braco koji te gleda u oči.

1997
01:48:08,319 --> 01:48:09,760
[SPEAKER_00] A, postojiš i ti.

1998
01:48:09,760 --> 01:48:15,600
[SPEAKER_00] Naš vjerni pratitelj, prijatelju, hvala ti na...

1999
01:48:15,600 --> 01:48:16,840
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala tebi na pozivu.

2000
01:48:16,840 --> 01:48:17,800
[SPEAKER_00] Na razgovoru.

2001
01:48:17,800 --> 01:48:19,960
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala ti što je ovo bilo zadnje pitanje.

2002
01:48:19,960 --> 01:48:21,159
[SPEAKER_01] Eto, ništa.

2003
01:48:21,159 --> 01:48:22,640
[SPEAKER_00] Nadam se da nisi previše patio.

2004
01:48:22,640 --> 01:48:23,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ne.

2005
01:48:23,039 --> 01:48:25,899
[SPEAKER_00] Htio si patit, pa vidim da želiš patit.

2006
01:48:25,899 --> 01:48:27,159
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne moram ju upražnjavati.

2007
01:48:27,159 --> 01:48:29,340
[SPEAKER_01] Svakodne, ono, rekli smo da vrijednosti nisu,

2008
01:48:29,340 --> 01:48:32,659
[SPEAKER_01] ono, nužne, vrline, mogu postati mane.

2009
01:48:32,659 --> 01:48:36,020
[SPEAKER_01] Ja moram primijetiti da si startao cijelu priču

2010
01:48:36,020 --> 01:48:37,439
[SPEAKER_01] sa pet očaka na papiru.

2011
01:48:37,819 --> 01:48:40,020
[SPEAKER_01] Sada je papir u potpunosti ispunjen.

2012
01:48:40,020 --> 01:48:43,720
[SPEAKER_01] Što samo govori o tvoje pripreme ili manjku iz tebe.

2013
01:48:43,720 --> 01:48:44,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ali hvala ti.

2014
01:48:44,460 --> 01:48:45,279
[SPEAKER_00] Šta će mi priprema?

2015
01:48:45,279 --> 01:48:46,500
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala ti puno.

2016
01:48:46,500 --> 01:48:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Planirao sam da ćemo raditi ovdje.

2017
01:48:48,000 --> 01:48:50,840
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala ti na dobroj igri.

2018
01:48:50,840 --> 01:48:52,300
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala tebi.

2019
01:48:52,300 --> 01:48:55,659
[SPEAKER_00] Nastavljamo uz neke rakice u uveći.

2020
01:48:55,659 --> 01:48:57,119
[SPEAKER_00] A ti, ništa.

2021
01:48:57,119 --> 01:48:58,539
[SPEAKER_00] Vidimo se za tijedan dana opet.

2022
01:48:58,539 --> 01:48:58,760
[SPEAKER_00] Bok.

